(83, 'SNEmul', '200 OK', 724, 'http://snemul.free.fr/', NULL, NULL, 'SNEmul is a brand new Super NES Emulator for the PC. Which means that this software is (in theory ;) able to run ROM-images of the SNES cartridges on your PC. In the long run, SNEmul should be a full SNES workbench with a debugger, an assembler/disassembler, and many other useful functions.', 'Emulation', 'Nintendo', NULL, 0, '2002-02-12 00:00:00', 0),
