(227, 'Noir', '200 OK', 718, 'http://www.noir.org', NULL, NULL, 'Noir is an art group that started in 1997 from a couple members of a dieing group called Overdose. During remained a solid stable group up releasing 14 amazing packs featuring some big names such as Dzeni and Plecxus. In 2000 Noir went idle and stayed that way until 2002. We are now back and better then ever. With over 70 members, Noir now represents some of the best professional established artists and upcoming artists out there.', 'Art', 'Group', 3, 0, '2003-08-27 00:00:00', 0),
