(250, 'Demo Vibes', '302 Found - <a href="http://planet-d.net/404.html">http://planet-d.net/404.html</a>', 394, 'http://willbe.planet-d.net/demovibes.htm', NULL, NULL, 'Demovibes is a mixed compilation of the finest demoscene electronic music. Designed to fit on three 80 minutes CD-R''s, its aim is to reach new audiences, external from demoscene.\r\n\r\nThe tracks selected here are not necessarely the most popular ones, but they represent a large spectrum of musical streams that have motivated many active demomakers from early 90''s to nowadays.', 'Art', 'Commercial', 4, -1, '2005-07-14 00:00:00', -1),
