(276, 'BitFellas', NULL, 3128, 'http://www.bitfellas.org', NULL, NULL, 'The BitFellas are providing the demoscene with a community portal and content\r\n database for almost all platforms, combined with a nice steadily moderated \r\n forum to exchange the latest gossip and information. We don''t intend to \r\n compete with other resources. We prefer to provide additional content and \r\n information. BF has been developed by a dedicated team of demoscene enthusiasts to provide an outstanding experience. Most of us have been involved in scene related \r\n operations and activities for very long time.', 'Art', 'News', 5, 0, '2006-09-03 00:00:00', 0),
